Klant: Yeah, the Autobots. How fascinating. A kid?

Klant looked puzzled, but then smiled.

Klant: One of our Maximals brought in a kid, before his group within the
Maximals ran him off. But we should no longer be concerned about the
Maximals. We should take our stuff and never darken their doors again, I
suppose...
